* Against my window *

40:49.064 --> 40:51.700
* Bringing back sweet memories *

40:52.968 --> 40:56.004
* Hey, windowpane *

40:56.138 --> 40:58.774
* Do you remember *

41:01.109 --> 41:04.046
* How sweet it used to be? *

41:07.883 --> 41:11.319
* When we was together *

41:13.488 --> 41:16.224
* Everything was so grand *

41:19.394 --> 41:23.699
* Now that we parted *

41:23.832 --> 41:26.001
* There's just one sound *

41:26.134 --> 41:28.871
* That I just can't stand *

41:29.004 --> 41:31.674
* I can't stand the rain *

41:32.808 --> 41:34.810
* Against my window *

41:36.945 --> 41:39.347
* Bringing back sweet memories *

41:40.849 --> 41:43.952
* I can't stand the rain *

41:44.086 --> 41:47.089
* Against my window *

41:48.924 --> 41:51.860
* 'Cause he's not here with me *

41:55.197 --> 41:59.267
* Whoa, empty pillow *

42:01.103 --> 42:04.039
* Where his head used to lay *

42:06.875 --> 42:11.379
* I know you've got
